\begin{explanation}
    1) and 2) are done\\
    \begin{itemize}
        \item $\| u + v \|^2 = \|u\|^2 + 2<u,v> + \|v\|^2 \le \|u\|^2 + 2\|u\|\|v\| + \|v\|^2 = (\|u\| + \|v\|)^2$
            \[
            \implies \|u + v\|^2 \le \|u\|^2 + \|v\|^2
            \] 
    \end{itemize}
\end{explanation}